<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-164] Fix junit related build issues</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-164</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since the junit switch no xml report files are generated and the build doesn&apos;t fail properly if a test fails&lt;/p&gt;</description>
